  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of the study is to test the effects of a herbal supplement, Phytalgic, on the
      symptoms of osteoarthritis of the knee or hip, in patients with OA using NSAIDs or analgesics
      on a regular basis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
